T02D1701:57a-4: rig byed sgrol ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1701:57a-5: gang zhig rmongs pas blo mdongs pa //
T02D1701:57a-6: rig byed sgrol ma rig pa'i mchog / rgyal po khyim bdag mgu byed pa //
T02D1701:57a-7: blang phyir bdag gis bri bar bya //
T02D1701:57a-8: gzhan yang sgrol ma'i rig pa mchog blang pa'i slad
T02D1701:57a-9: du bsnyen ba'i grangs tshad du song zhing sgrub thabs
T02D1701:57a-10: cho ga blo 'dris pa'i rten gyi gang zag gis
T02D1701:57a-11: byams pa dang snying rje sngon du bskyed la skad
T02D1701:57a-12: cig gis rig byed sgrol ma sku mdog tshos chen
T02D1701:57a-13: po lta bu zhal gcig phyag bzhi pa /
T02D1701:57a-14: g-yas kyi dang po mi 'jigs pa'i phyag dang /
T02D1701:57a-16: g-yon gyis rin po che'i gzhu dang /
T02D1701:57a-17: g-yon gnyis bas autpala dmar po 'dzin pa /
T02D1701:57a-18: rgyan sna tshogs kyis sbras pa /
T02D1701:57a-19: padma dang zla ba'i gdan la skyil krung gis bzhugs pa /
T02D1701:57a-20: de'i thugs kar pam las padma /
T02D1701:57a-21: aa las zla ba'i steng du t'am dmar po byi ru'i mdog lta bu las /
T02D1701:57a-22: phyogs bcur 'od 'phros tshur bsdus nas bdag gi kun
T02D1701:57a-23: du rmongs pa'i tshogs thams cad zhi bar bsam zhing
T02D1701:57a-24: sems gtad la bsgom par bya'o //
T02D1701:57a-25: de nas skye bar gyur na gsang sngags rgyun mgal
T02D1701:57a-26: me'i 'khor lo lta bus sems sbyangs nas yar ngo'i
T02D1701:57a-27: chos brgyad kyi nyin par nas mtshal dang gur gum
T02D1701:57a-28: dang gi wam rnams sbyar la padma 'dab ma bcu
T02D1701:57b-0: @57b aom t'a re tu tt'a re aa ni bhi pra dzny'a s'a dha na /
T02D1701:57b-1: aa bhi bra dzny'a pra s'a dha sv'a h'a /
T02D1701:57b-2: zhes bzla zhing bdag dang 'khor lo phan tshun thim zhing snying po dang gzungs dgod //
T02D1701:57b-3: 'khor lo gcig la dbyangs dang gsal byed bri bar bya'o //
T02D1701:57b-4: de nas bco lnga'i mtshan phyed la zla ba la
T02D1701:57b-5: mngon du phyogs pas mchod pa rnam pa lnga dang
T02D1701:57b-6: sbyin sreg dang gtor ma rnams phul la /
T02D1701:57b-7: me long g-y'a yongs su dag pa bug med pa
T02D1701:57b-8: la sindh'u ra dmar po mandala la gser ram zangs
T02D1701:57b-9: kyi thur mas 'khor lo ji lta ba bzhin du
T02D1701:57b-10: phyi nang du gnyis bris la snying po dang gzungs
T02D1701:57b-11: dang / phyi ma la dbyangs dang gsal byed bkod
T02D1701:57b-12: de cung zhig bzlas pa bya zhing mchod pa rnam
T02D1701:57b-13: pa lngas yang dag par mchod la 'khor lo gnyis
T02D1701:57b-14: dril te mgul du gdags par bya /
T02D1701:57b-15: sindhu ra legs par bsdus te dug lang ka wa
T02D1701:57b-16: ti'i sbu gur blugs la mchan khung g-yon par btags
T02D1701:57b-17: te thig le dmar po skra mtshams su bya zhing
T02D1701:57b-18: / bsod snyoms kyi phyir grong khyer du zhugs na
T02D1701:57b-19: rgyal po dang khyim bdag dad cing 'dun par 'gyur
T02D1701:57b-20: / ro // sgra dang bstan bcos mang po dang //
T02D1701:57b-21: rol mo sgyu rtsal ji snyed dang //
T02D1701:57b-22: lha dang gnod sbyin bu mo sogs //
T02D1701:57b-23: rig byed mthu yis 'dun par byed //
